:::Wheeljack:::

::He nods to Composer::
Wheeljack: Yes, that was her name.  She went to the Maximals with the story 
that she had been attacked by the Alliance, and they took her in.  Basically 
it was Zardus' idea that she would use her seductive charm to get inside of 
the Maximals, and though i have nothing against our leader, i think he made a 
mistake.  Skulletron also perished.
::He turns to Vamprah::
Wheeljack: Yes, i think you're ready to go. I hope you uncover a lot of info 
about the new Maximal City.

--part1_11d.4059267.28c2f74c_boundary
